'''偽黑盲蛛屬'''（{{lang|la|''Pseudomelanopa''}}）是[[蜘蛛綱|蜘蛛綱]]下的一個屬，屬於[[盲蛛目|盲蛛目]][[開氣門亞目|開氣門亞目]][[硬體盲蛛科|硬體盲蛛科]]<ref name=wanfang>{{cite journal |title=寧夏六盤偽黑盲蛛記述(盲蛛目,開氣門亞目,硬體盲蛛科) |url=http://d.wanfangdata.com.cn/periodical_dwfl200903003.aspx |year=2009 |authors=張超、朱明生 |journal=[[動物分類學報_(中國)|動物分類學報]] |volume=34 |issue=3 |language=zh-hans |access-date=2011-08-17 |archive-date=2012-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120318115904/http://d.wanfangdata.com.cn/periodical_dwfl200903003.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。過往，蜘蛛學家認為本屬只有唯一種類，亦即[[臺灣偽黑盲蛛|臺灣偽黑盲蛛]]<ref>{{cite web |editor=Joel Hallan |url=http://insects.tamu.edu/research/collection/hallan/Acari/Family/Sclerosomatidae.txt |title=Sclerosomatidae Species Listing |work=Biology Catalog |publisher=[[Texas_A&M_University|Texas A&M University]] |accessdate=2010-12-27 |language=en |archive-date=2014-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141013064709/https://insects.tamu.edu/research/collection/hallan/Acari/Family/Sclerosomatidae.txt |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但自從2009年中國大陸的學者在[[寧夏|寧夏]]發現了[[六盤偽黑盲蛛|六盤偽黑盲蛛]]之後，這個屬從此多了一位新成員<ref name=wanfang />。

